Description:
Superbly spacious with captivating outlooks
Enjoying the privilege of a top floor position overlooking the leafy streetscape, this instantly inviting residence combines light filled spaciousness with supreme urban convenience. The impressive dimensions of the open plan living and dining space immediately engage you upon entering this stylish apartment with brand new carpets. Adjoining the living area, a north east facing balcony provides lovely green vistas and glimpses of the Dandenong Ranges, offering the perfect space for relaxed dining and entertaining. In its own bright zone a contemporary kitchen presents Miele appliances including gas cooktop and dishwasher. Two generous bedrooms are each fitted with mirror built in robes, including the main with an ensuite. Also includes a practical bathroom, European laundry, secure undercover parking, intercom entry and heating. In a peaceful setting, yet offering easy access to South Yarra Station, Toorak Road trams and restaurants plus the Botanical Gardens and Yarra River trails.

Description:
Prestigious Penthouse, Stunning Skyline Perspective
In a league of its own, this exceptionally large and captivating, two bedroom penthouse apartment combines stunning views with a breath-taking indoor-outdoor connection and an edgy designer personality. Sitting proudly at the pinnacle of inner-urban apartment living, the home is directly opposite The Jam Factory and comes with the promise of an exciting Chapel St lifestyle as well as unforgettable home entertaining.
Two sets of double glass, sliding doors connect the vast open-plan kitchen / meals / living to the home's enormous, north and east facing, wrap-around balcony as it introduces the urban panorama and Melbourne skyline as a welcome guest to this impressive home. Caesar Stone benches, mirror splash backs and soft close cabinetry indicate commitment to quality that compliments the views and transcends the home. Secure parking, video entry and elevator access are befitting of this premier address, and the home also offers a master bedroom with ensuite, mirrored bedroom robes, sleek bathroom / laundry and reverse cycle air conditioning.
A penthouse within metres of all the cafes, bars, restaurants and iconic strip of boutique shopping on Chapel St is a rare privilege indeed. Directly opposite the Jam Factory's cinemas and moments from trams and South Yarra Train Station further highlight the joy of this location.

Description:
Parkside and private. Melbourne on your doorstep
A magnificent elevated location in the tightly held Pasley Street precinct, overlooking Fawkner Park, provides the setting for this outstanding contemporary apartment of generous proportions, filled with natural light. An undercover west facing terrace establishes the vantage point from which to enjoy views of acres of parkland and enables indoor outdoor living all year round. Full width open plan living provides zones for relaxing and formal dining and a sizeable kitchen also includes space for meals. Two expansive bedrooms, the triple robed main bedroom complete with ensuite, are complemented by a stylish central powder room and second bathroom. Also includes laundry, heating and cooling, storage, parking and secure entry via a private courtyard within an established development. A fabulous lifestyle location within excellent proximity of transport links, Chapel Street and South Yarra shops and cafes, St Kilda Road and Albert Park.

Description:
A Luxe Lifestyle with Spectacular Panoramic Views
Delivering spectacular panoramic views, flawless style, premium quality plus a vibrant location, this luxurious apartment positioned on the twelfth floor of the north-west corner within the newly completed Yarra House will not disappoint. Every element has been designed, crafted, finished to perfection and positioned to take full advantage of views that span from the Macedon Ranges, across the city skyline to Port Phillip Bay. The stunning three bedroom (BIRs), two bathroom apartment boasts an open plan kitchen equipped with an integrated dish-drawer, Gaggenau gas cooktop and oven, stone benchtops and a moveable island bench. A generous living and dining zone with floor to ceiling glass offering a northerly view over prestigious Melbourne High School’s sports grounds, the Yarra River and beyond opens to a large wrap-around balcony. With inclusions such as a European laundry, three secure basement carspaces, a storage cage, double glazed windows, blockout blinds, reverse cycle heating/cooling and video intercom as well as resort style facilities incorporating an infinity edge lap pool, steam room, gym, entertaining deck, business centre, library and lift access, this residence offers a superb opportunity in an extremely convenient location with South Yarra Station, cafes, shops, trams and the Yarra River bike trails all on the doorstep.

Penthouse Exclusivity, Refined Entertaining Luxury
Rising at the apex of Melbourne’s most cosmopolitan quarters, this luxurious penthouse crowns the entire top-floor of the bespoke European inspired “The Lowndes” development hidden between Toorak Road and Chapel Street.
Style focused and gallery inspired, the four bedroom, 4.5 bathroom plus a study residence is wrapped in beautiful entertaining terraces and enhanced by memorable elevated views over Melbourne.
Grandly scaled and beautifully detailed with soaring ceilings, travertine and hardwood flooring and floor-to-ceiling glass doors, the apartment is a stage for both large scale entertaining and intimate daily living.
Stunning formal and informal living rooms with a central bar are illuminated in northern light each with bi-fold doors opening the rooms to a beautiful northern entertaining terrace shaded beneath a vine draped pergola. A separate dining room and granite kitchen with Paul Bocuse freestanding stove lead out to an expansive deck backdropped by blue skies and birds eye aspects over South Yarra’s leafy streetscapes.
The four bedrooms, three with bespoke ensuites, all open to the terraces including the palatial hotel inspired north-facing main bedroom suite with dressing room, gym and tranquil study.
Expertly designed and impeccably detailed, appointments include basement garaging for three cars, direct lift access into your own private foyer, remarkable seamless storage, cellar, powder room, heating, air conditioning and separate laundry.
Within a minute’s walk of Toorak Road and Chapel Street’s restaurants, vibrant cafes, boutique shops and trams, the apartment is also located within a short stroll of South Yarra station, Prahran Market, Como cinema, Fawner Park and the Yarra River.
Inspect by appointment

Description:
Luxury, Panoramic Views and a Prime Location
Embracing panoramic views across Melbourne from the MCG over to Port Phillip Bay, the city skyline and everything in between, this superb apartment on the eighth floor epitomises contemporary inner city living. Beautifully finished with an exacting attention to detail, this exclusive community offers a dress circle lifestyle like no other. Situated in the highly sought after Society complex which boasts lift access, concierge, library, cinema, lounge, gymnasium, outdoor terrace and two spas all for resident use, the west-facing apartment offers spacious and modern interiors. Comprising of an open plan kitchen equipped with quality appliances including dish-drawer, lounge and dining with balcony, master bedroom with study or storage nook and built in robes, second bedroom with built in robes and a stylish bathroom with an oversized shower. A European laundry, video intercom, reverse cycle heating/cooling and secure off street parking ensure this is an absolute dream property for those seeking a private oasis nestled amongst the heart of South Yarra's entertainment district with the Jam Factory cinemas, nightlife, boutique shops, trams and Prahran Market moments away.

Description:
Unbelievable investment, extremely good value Townhouse (Only 3 minutes walk to Chapel St)
Absolutely charming townhouse in it's original structure posses a lavish depth of character due to the extra ceiling height and the aesthetic. With universally high quality finishes, each property has its own distinct footprint which ensures no two interiors are alike. Tucked away in a quiet cul-de-sac, private & secure with enclose court yard and strolling distance to South Yarra's fashion designers and artists, bookshops and cinemas, specialist food stores and markets, trendy upmarket shopping on famous Toorak Road and Chapel Street, restaurants and cafes.
EAT, PLAY, SHOP & STAY in South Yarra.
South Yarra is one of the most liveable suburb due to good proximity to the CBD, schools, cafes and restaurants; access to trains, trams, and buses; and abundance of open spaces and trees.
South Yarra offers great public transportation with two railway stations. South Yarra railway station and Hawksburn Station. Tram routes 58, 72 and 78 also run through South Yarra. Major bus routes run along Commercial Road and Punt Road.
Top school precinct with Melbourne High School, Melbourne Girls Grammar School Merton Hall campus is located in South Yarra & few minutes drive from Melbourne Grammar School on St Kilda Road. Christ Church Grammar School and South Yarra Primary School, two of Victoria's oldest primary schools, are also located in South Yarra.
Why buy an apartment when you can own a landed property for similar amount of money? And pay low body corporate with huge potential growth.
This is definitely a unique product. We have a serious seller however there will only be one lucky buyer to make this HOME.

A fabulous lifestyle choice and an excellent investment, this stylish and spacious town residence is superbly located on the doorstep of Hawksburn Village, handy to a plethora of dining options, prestige retailers, trams and Hawksburn Station. Just minutes from Chapel St and Toorak Rd shops, dine and entertainment precinct, this superb apartment have the best of what the suburbs can offer. 2 bedroom apartment with a pleasant courtyard view. Each room is carpeted and completed with a B.I.R. Modern kitchen with stone bench top, glass splashback and stainless steel appliances. Resident of this apartment will have unlimited access to the building's 5 star facilities such as:
- Indoor heated swimming pool
- Gym
- Spa and Sauna
- Tennis Court
- BBQ area
- Concierge
Find everything at your door step, from grocery shopping at Woolworths and Big W just, morning coffees and breakfast at the spectacular cafes on the ground floor of the building or around the area; Tram stop and South Yarra train station can be reached within just minutes of walk. Car space is included.
Contact us today to inspect the property!
Please bring your proof of identity (i.e. driver's license, passport) when attending our open for inspection.

Description:
Flexible floorplan, convenient location
Beautifully bright and remarkably peaceful, this two storey town residence designed by architect Neil Clerehan, offers an easily maintained haven surrounded by vibrant lifestyle amenities. Arranged in a versatile floorplan, this home is ready to respond to the requirements of the residents with an array of flexible spaces. The ground floor features an inviting living area, practical kitchen and open plan dining area enhanced by outlooks of the verdant courtyard, perfectly appointed for sundrenched alfresco dining. Generous accommodation comprises two superb ensuite bedrooms and a refined study which could serve as a third bedroom if desired. Comprehensive features include powder room, intercom, split system air conditioning, laundry facilities and garage parking. Only moments from a host of shops and cafes on Toorak Road, Fawkner Park, trams and South Yarra station providing an easy commute to the CBD.

Welcome to the ultimate cosmopolitan lifestyle just a step away from Chapel Street in the heart of the stunning, sophisticated South Yarra. Noir Apartments are perfectly located next to the iconic Jam Factory.
> Brand new apartments complete and ready to move in
> Exceptional value with discount incentives being offered

> Low owners corporation fees
> Designed by award-winning firm CHT Architects

Designed by award-winning firm CHT Architects, Noir takes its place in one of South Yarra’s most notable addresses with a signature building distinguished by a visually arresting facade of interlocking geometries. Don’t miss this opportunity to live and breathe Chapel Street and what this glamorous neighbourhood has to offer.

Description:
Value $780,000 Sunsets, City Views and Great Spaces
Indulge in spectacular views of the city skyline, South Yarra high rises and the charming slate roofs of historic homes below from the 4th floor of this sun filled 2 bedroom 2 bathroom security apartment.
Big on space and brilliant on potential, this apartment classic enjoys a renovated stone kitchen with granite island bench and some new appliances, overlooking the generous living & dining area; a covered west-facing balcony with adjoining enclosed; 2 double bedrooms (BIRs) including main with a WIR and original ensuite; vintage bathroom and a separate laundry with storage.
With ample storage throughout, this urban classic is something you can slowly renovate to your own taste while enjoying the modern comforts of R/C air conditioning, a security intercom and an auto lock up garage.
In this sought after position with the tram at your door to take you to the MCG, theatre, work or fine restaurants, halfway between Toorak Village and Chapel Street chic, minutes to Hawksburn station, stately Como House, the Yarra River and excellent schools.

Description:
Inner City Living in Lifestyle Central
Sleek, stylish and sun-drenched, this architect designed contemporary residence, over three levels, shows stunning dimensions delivering immeasurable lifestyle appeal literally metres from Prahran Market and the vast array of cafes, restaurants and boutiques on Chapel St and Commercial Rd.
Bathed in northern light and featuring timber floors, the open-plan living and dining room together with a gourmet kitchen appointed with stone benches and Miele appliances open to a wide north-facing covered balcony, perfect for al fresco dining and entertainment. A versatile floorplan offers main bedroom with north facing balcony and stunning city views, stylish en-suite, built in robe and mezzanine study serenely situated on its own level, while on the ground level two additional double bedrooms with built in robes and a chic bathroom open to a private courtyard.
Superbly presented for immediate enjoyment, it also includes a stylish powder-room, generous laundry, ample storage, hydronic heating & reverse cycle cooling, internally accessed garage and additional off street parking.
Walking distance to public transport and everything you need right on your doorstep.

Description:
Oversized, Resort-Style Luxury designed & built by Mirvac
Perfectly poised on the fringe of Chapel St, this securely-gated, modern, oversized two bedroom apartment offers a remarkable sense of sanctuary and sets the benchmark for inner-urban living. Adjacent to both Chapel St and Toorak Rd, this Mirvac built apartment is beautifully presented and combines its sizable proportions with a lap pool, gymnasium, sauna and spa. Opening attractively to a full width balcony with lovely views over palm trees, this superb apartment features open-plan living with premium stainless steel appliances, wrap-around kitchen bench, as well as the privilege of a master bedroom, with ensuite and bath. Securely accessed by intercom entry, the home also presents buyers with the highly-coveted prize of secure basement parking for one vehicle, a convenient storage cage and elevator access. Almost surreal in the tranquillity it offers, this sophisticated apartment is set at the back of the block amongst large communal grounds, just a few steps from an amazing range of strip shops, cafes, restaurants, bars, cinemas and an abundance of public transport to give you a rich lifestyle coloured by cosmopolitan diversity.
